***  NO SUBTITLING ***
  THIS STORY IS GOOD.  THE ACTING IS EXCELLENT, AND IT NEEDS TO BE. BECAUSE THE PRODUCERS DIDN'T PUT ANY SUBTITLING FOR US TO SEE.
I DON'T SPEAK PINOY AND WHAT LITTLE ENGLISH THE ACTORS SAY DOES HELP
  I WOULD HAVE GIVEN IT A 5 STARS IF THEY HAD PUT SUBTITLING FOR EVERYONE TO REALLY UNDERSTAND WHATS GOING ON.
